                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>I suppose he finds[...]<lb/> to print them I h[...]<lb/> nor have I\n                                        ever heard [...]<lb/> abundance of material [...]<lb/>\n                                        volume might be arranged [...]<lb/> account of the Jews in\n                                                  <placeName>Spain</placeName>\n                                        <placeName>Portugal</placeName> [...]<lb/> information on\n                                        the same subject in Mr [...]</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The enclosed reflection I for[...]<lb/> as my\n                                        former writings they are at you[...]<lb/> they can be of any\n                                        use to our [...]<lb/> may have to discuss with [...]<lb/>\n                                        the scheme of Christianity. as I refer[...]<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Bishop of <placeName>London</placeName></persName>\n                                        to the Creeds of the [...]<lb/> sent you those two\n                                        document). loose who [...]<lb/> them from passage) as my\n                                        vouchers for [...]<lb/> my reflections I shall be happy to\n                                        [...]<lb/> to say that your prospects have become\n                                        brig[...]<lb/> my utmost isolated position does not\n                                        aff[...]<lb/> of being [?] to you I remain with you[...]</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(8)\">Reverend Sir your's[...]</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(10)\">[?]</p>"
